<fragment-cfabee1a-3db3-4b38-ad57-b63b962fc5fb """
Welcome Club Captain!
""">

<fragment-3cc7113a-579e-42f5-8fd6-a7e5b2da02f1 """
Thanks for your interest in being a Mozilla Club Captain and hosting a Mozilla Club for your local community.
""">

<fragment-6bd7363d-7cf7-45aa-a623-1a6b5f44a9a0 """
This is an incredible opportunity for you to empower your learners with important web skills by guiding them through seriously fun activities. You will also grow as you teach, improving your facilitation and web skills as you go.
""">

<fragment-f81f27c9-45ea-47d7-933e-d5c202e0454e """
In this package you will find:
""">

<fragment-338d10e0-904b-4bd5-873a-b35c1cab2c4d """
a guide for your first month as a Club Captain.
""">

<fragment-e41994ff-637f-474a-95c5-056b51b62021 """
a pledge to sign and send back to your Regional Coordinator.
""">

<fragment-0e37e7d1-0cf2-464c-96ca-0ce7af97b53a """
If you have any questions please contact your Regional Coordinator. If you still have issues email <a href="mailto:teachtheweb@mozillafoundation.org">teachtheweb@mozillafoundation.org</a>.
""">

<fragment-3481b052-6ba2-4604-99ae-cd089f9debec """
We can&#x2019;t wait to #teachtheweb with you!
""">

<fragment-4ed5464d-231d-4b15-b4bb-c98906b2bad4 """
Your first month at a glance:
""">

<fragment-26947ab2-dc22-410e-8a85-5be25ab49066 """
<strong>Pledge to host your Mozilla Club [Week 1]</strong>
""">

<fragment-a233d895-7c55-4712-87f6-763c39ddcf62 """
Review the <a href="http://mozilla.github.io/learning-networks/clubs/">Mozilla Club fact sheet.</a>
""">

<fragment-cd59c87d-1868-4937-bb2b-2526919c5970 """
Do an interview with a Regional Coordinator to complete your pledge.
""">

<fragment-981f3cdb-c455-4666-9775-242475937f94 """
Share your goals with peers and discuss steps needed to achieve them.
""">

<fragment-c44f1666-2283-491f-81bc-5e1857a30082 """
<strong>Prepare your team, your learners and your space [Week 2 - 3]</strong>
""">

<fragment-b8046713-00d7-4096-8c4f-4012f25f5e68 """
<a href="https://d157rqmxrxj6ey.cloudfront.net/mozillalearning/17695/">Name your club</a> and find a team.
""">

<fragment-5a24bc49-5e6b-4795-baf3-13d41c49af6b """
Schedule your first three sessions and invite your learners.
""">

<fragment-6cec4cd8-163a-4c00-ac4b-fd5b2d297910 """
Ensure a safe, welcoming environment.
""">

<fragment-0e22d0f8-3313-4760-bedc-7f53d8c84540 """
<strong>Host your first sessions [Week 4]</strong>
""">

<fragment-793d06db-b73f-43b0-b027-cc68d9d0c3c8 """
Select your favorite teaching activities from <a href="https://teach.mozilla.org/activities/">Mozilla&#x2019;s collection.</a>
""">

<fragment-416b3bbe-937c-48fc-88af-45a99a99914b """
Practice teaching the activities with your team, and then teach it to your learners.
""">

<fragment-910e5e21-e879-466a-98b1-3ed4d56e6577 """
After each session, <a href="http://discourse.webmaker.org/category/clubs">share your experience</a> with fellow Club Captains in our discussion forum and with your Regional Coordinator during your regular calls.
